      • setup

        public void setup()
        Description copied from interface: BentoBoxCommand
        Setups anything that is needed for this command.

        It is recommended you do the following in this method:
        • Register any of the sub-commands of this command;
        • Define the permission required to use this command using CompositeCommand.setPermission(String);
        • Define whether this command can only be run by players or not using CompositeCommand.setOnlyPlayer(boolean);
